TFP, really felt the nerves and your breath on my neck! Good luck in the remaining part of the tournament

Later on very empty side zones, no topias, no gold banks. TP without any roll but first Earth around 1/3/1 for me on Crag, so opp was already jumping joyfully. First TP I used happened to be in 1/3/5 (sic!), but luckily the years of experience made me come on top. Nice game from my opp's side, GL in the tournament!
